1
00:00:00,510 --> 00:00:02,040
(All characters, locations,
organizations, and incidents...)

2
00:00:02,040 --> 00:00:03,540
(in this drama are fictional.)

3
00:00:03,540 --> 00:00:05,080
(This production followed
all guidelines for young actors.)

4
00:00:18,490 --> 00:00:19,560
A Reum.

5
00:00:21,830 --> 00:00:23,030
Mommy will protect you.

6
00:00:24,100 --> 00:00:26,160
(Shocking Footage: Kunhyang Group's
Honorary Chairman Jin Tae Seok...)

7
00:00:26,160 --> 00:00:27,630
(Pushes Person off Roof)

8
00:00:27,700 --> 00:00:29,030
(Uploading...)

9
00:00:29,970 --> 00:00:31,100
What are you doing here?

10
00:00:37,510 --> 00:00:38,510
Young Chae...

11
00:00:39,780 --> 00:00:42,050
- What have you done?
- What needed to be done.

12
00:00:42,580 --> 00:00:44,080
Jin Tae Seok
made a fool of you and me...

13
00:00:46,020 --> 00:00:47,020
No...

14
00:00:49,090 --> 00:00:53,090
I'll make sure he pays a heavy price
for messing with our A Reum.

15
00:00:56,730 --> 00:00:59,560
You're telling me Madam Gong
took half of the slush fund?

16
00:01:00,470 --> 00:01:01,770
I heard it from her myself.

17
00:01:02,500 --> 00:01:03,770
She's not the type
to just give it back.

18
00:01:04,700 --> 00:01:06,040
What are you going to do?

19
00:01:07,210 --> 00:01:09,910
What's more important is
who has the Swiss account.

20
00:01:10,710 --> 00:01:13,750
All Gong Nan Sook
cares about is the money.

21
00:01:19,450 --> 00:01:21,850
There's something you need to see.
It's a video of Cha Jung Won.

22
00:01:22,250 --> 00:01:24,360
(Shocking Footage: Kunhyang Group's
Honorary Chairman Jin Tae Seok...)

23
00:01:24,360 --> 00:01:25,620
(Pushes Person off Roof)

24
00:01:30,700 --> 00:01:32,060
Who on earth would do
something like this?

25
00:01:34,570 --> 00:01:38,300
Young Chae had the original file
on her phone.

26
00:01:38,540 --> 00:01:41,570
So you're saying
Joo Young Chae did this?

27
00:01:41,940 --> 00:01:43,410
Se Hoon must have known
about it too.

28
00:01:43,610 --> 00:01:44,940
They must've shared it.

29
00:01:55,250 --> 00:01:57,620
Sir, the video of you pushing
Cha Jung Won off the rooftop...

30
00:01:57,690 --> 00:01:58,820
I'm watching it now.

31
00:01:59,620 --> 00:02:00,660
That's not all.

32
00:02:06,460 --> 00:02:07,470
What?

33
00:02:08,670 --> 00:02:11,070
"The death penalty
for attempted murder?"

34
00:02:12,170 --> 00:02:14,770
A national petition
to have me executed?

35
00:02:17,710 --> 00:02:19,680
Who has the audacity
to pull something like this?

36
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:28,190
You're buying me lunch?
What's the occasion?

37
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,090
Young Chae.

38
00:02:35,390 --> 00:02:37,200
I feel really sorry.

39
00:02:38,830 --> 00:02:42,370
Instead of comforting you,
I kept telling you that you were wrong.

40
00:02:42,700 --> 00:02:44,940
Just act like you always do.
Let's keep it real.

41
00:02:47,570 --> 00:02:49,670
What? Why?

42
00:02:50,540 --> 00:02:51,680
What are you getting at?

43
00:02:52,340 --> 00:02:53,610
Did you post the video...

44
00:02:55,110 --> 00:02:56,110
of Jung Won's accident?

45
00:02:59,150 --> 00:03:01,720
I gave the original file
from the rooftop to Se Hoon.

46
00:03:01,990 --> 00:03:03,420
So you're saying Se Hoon is the one
who posted it?

47
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:05,790
He wouldn't have done that.

48
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:07,960
Because...

49
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:11,030
he's a total mess right now.

50
00:03:11,030 --> 00:03:12,400
So are you.

51
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:14,800
Stop beating around the bush
and just tell me the truth.

52
00:03:15,270 --> 00:03:17,800
Maybe Se Hoon and I
posted it together?

53
00:03:18,170 --> 00:03:19,170
I can't seem to remember.

54
00:03:20,070 --> 00:03:21,270
I should get back
to the Design Team.

55
00:03:22,910 --> 00:03:25,010
They can't get anything done
without me.

56
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,820
She got fired from the Design Team
a while back.

57
00:03:39,590 --> 00:03:41,690
Director Jin.

58
00:03:44,730 --> 00:03:47,230
Is the sales statistics report ready?

59
00:03:48,530 --> 00:03:49,530
Yes.

60
00:03:52,740 --> 00:03:54,240
Is it true?

61
00:03:55,310 --> 00:03:57,280
Did the Honorary Chairman really
do that to Chief Director Cha?

62
00:03:57,810 --> 00:03:58,810
It's true.

63
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:04,150
It was all caught on camera,
so what's the point in denying it?

64
00:04:07,450 --> 00:04:10,960
But the Honorary Chairman
is your father, isn't he?

65
00:04:11,690 --> 00:04:12,860
I didn't know that at the time.

66
00:04:13,790 --> 00:04:16,790
- But even if you didn't know...
- That's still attempted murder.

67
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,830
What's this?
A meeting without the director?

68
00:04:22,770 --> 00:04:24,070
Has all discipline gone
out the window?

69
00:04:24,670 --> 00:04:26,200
- Young Chae.
- Young Chae.

70
00:04:26,940 --> 00:04:29,610
So, what about my new designs?
Everyone loves them, right?

71
00:04:32,710 --> 00:04:33,910
Why is everyone staring at me
like that?

72
00:04:34,550 --> 00:04:36,980
Young Chae, do you even realize
where you are?

73
00:04:37,250 --> 00:04:39,950
Of course I do. This is my office.

74
00:04:41,650 --> 00:04:46,620
I think Joo Young Chae
might need professional help...

75
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:49,930
Young Chae, you know
you're pregnant, don't you?

76
00:04:50,460 --> 00:04:51,730
Young Chae's pregnant?

77
00:04:52,260 --> 00:04:53,330
It's Se Hoon's baby.

78
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,970
The future heir
to the Kunhyang family.

79
00:04:56,930 --> 00:05:00,810
Young Chae, you should stay here
in the office and not wander off.

80
00:05:01,940 --> 00:05:03,010
Everyone's okay with that, right?

81
00:05:03,810 --> 00:05:05,040
We should help her,

82
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:07,280
especially since we know her
and she is having a hard time.

83
00:05:07,610 --> 00:05:09,650
- Right.
- Well...

84
00:05:10,950 --> 00:05:12,820
I'll hire you on a contract basis,

85
00:05:13,150 --> 00:05:16,050
so report to work here from now on.
Got it?

86
00:05:20,860 --> 00:05:24,000
Hey, this is the video of
Jin Tae Seok pushing Cha Jung Won...

87
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:26,130
- off the roof, right?
- Yes, ma'am.

88
00:05:26,660 --> 00:05:29,270
Hold on, didn't you say
Young Chae filmed this?

89
00:05:29,670 --> 00:05:31,440
That foolish girl.
She has got some nerve.

90
00:05:31,700 --> 00:05:33,870
What was she thinking,
posting something like this?

91
00:05:35,370 --> 00:05:38,210
What do you mean?
You have to deal with it for me.

92
00:05:39,110 --> 00:05:40,110
Come sit over here.

93
00:05:41,580 --> 00:05:43,580
Did you really do this?
Are you sure?

94
00:05:45,650 --> 00:05:46,650
What?

95
00:05:47,490 --> 00:05:49,390
Ms. Young Chae,
are you out of your mind?

96
00:05:50,050 --> 00:05:51,660
Hey, that's my line.

97
00:05:52,290 --> 00:05:55,130
I'm your puppet, aren't I?
So you figure it out for me.

98
00:05:55,190 --> 00:05:57,260
What exactly do you expect me
to do about it?

99
00:05:57,730 --> 00:06:00,130
The Swiss account,
the one Jin Tae Seok had.

100
00:06:00,470 --> 00:06:02,270
Se Hoon took it,
but then it was taken back from him.

101
00:06:02,900 --> 00:06:04,040
Mom, I need you to get it back.

102
00:06:04,770 --> 00:06:08,040
What do you mean?
I already took half of it.

103
00:06:08,210 --> 00:06:09,210
What?

104
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:12,080
You were the one
who changed the password?

105
00:06:12,580 --> 00:06:13,580
How much?

106
00:06:14,380 --> 00:06:16,210
You should've taken
all of the money.

107
00:06:16,910 --> 00:06:19,080
Who are you to lecture me?

108
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,150
Let's talk later.

109
00:06:21,150 --> 00:06:22,650
But you're sure the other half
is still there, right?

110
00:06:22,950 --> 00:06:23,960
Oh my.

111
00:06:24,890 --> 00:06:26,460
My head is spinning.

112
00:06:26,990 --> 00:06:30,230
What on earth
is that girl plotting now?

113
00:06:30,930 --> 00:06:32,600
It may be necessary
to seek medical assistance...

114
00:06:33,530 --> 00:06:36,570
I'm fine. It's not that serious.

115
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:39,770
I wasn't talking about you, ma'am.
I'm worried about Ms. Young Chae.

116
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,040
Why you...

117
00:06:42,970 --> 00:06:44,540
- Oh my...
- Be careful...

118
00:06:45,580 --> 00:06:48,250
Is my Jung Won going to be okay?

119
00:06:49,210 --> 00:06:52,980
Is it true that Jin Se Hoon
tried to poison Jin Tae Seok?

120
00:06:53,550 --> 00:06:54,550
Yes, he did.

121
00:06:54,650 --> 00:06:56,350
And Jung Won switched the bottles...

122
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:57,860
and pretended to drink
the poisoned one herself.

123
00:06:59,020 --> 00:07:01,190
Then that means Jin Tae Seok...

124
00:07:01,690 --> 00:07:03,930
will trust my Jung Won
more now, right?

125
00:07:04,260 --> 00:07:05,330
Chairman Jin Tae Seok...

126
00:07:06,300 --> 00:07:08,600
is incapable of trusting anyone.

127
00:07:09,900 --> 00:07:13,270
There's no telling
when he'll change his mind again.

128
00:07:14,070 --> 00:07:16,440
Unbelievable.
What kind of man is he?

129
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,640
That's who he really is.

130
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:21,950
He doesn't trust anyone,

131
00:07:21,950 --> 00:07:24,150
so he's always hiding a knife
behind his back.

132
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,880
Of all the people in the world,

133
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:28,520
how could a monster like that
be Jung Won's father?

134
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,120
Oh, dear.

135
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:35,830
Listen, Manager Hwang.

136
00:07:36,260 --> 00:07:37,430
Yes, Mi Hyang?

137
00:07:38,230 --> 00:07:41,070
Please, I need you
to protect Jung Won.

138
00:07:41,670 --> 00:07:42,770
Can you promise me that?

139
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:46,340
I already lost
my daughter Jo Jung Won,

140
00:07:47,100 --> 00:07:50,440
and I don't want to lose
the daughter I have now.

141
00:07:53,380 --> 00:07:56,650
You're the only one I can ask.

142
00:07:57,920 --> 00:08:00,790
I will protect Cha Jung Won...

143
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:03,150
with my life.

144
00:08:05,090 --> 00:08:06,120
Thank you.

145
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:15,430
(Chief Kim Ji Hwan)

146
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:28,550
You're calling me often these days,
Chief Kim.

147
00:08:33,220 --> 00:08:36,020
That video from the rooftop?
It's a complete fabrication.

148
00:08:36,090 --> 00:08:37,120
You know...

149
00:08:37,460 --> 00:08:39,920
people are after my power,

150
00:08:39,990 --> 00:08:41,960
and they try to undermine me
every chance they get.

151
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:44,360
How could you let a video
like that surface?

152
00:08:44,930 --> 00:08:46,730
A father pushes his own daughter
from a rooftop...

153
00:08:47,730 --> 00:08:49,170
It's too gruesome
to even talk about.

154
00:08:49,470 --> 00:08:50,670
And that's not all.

155
00:08:50,670 --> 00:08:52,540
There's even a public petition
calling for the death penalty.

156
00:08:52,540 --> 00:08:54,170
I saw it.

157
00:08:55,340 --> 00:08:58,610
They can bark all they want,
but they can't mess with me.

158
00:08:58,740 --> 00:09:01,310
I'll take care of everything.
Just give me some time.

159
00:09:01,380 --> 00:09:03,480
You're putting the old man
in a bind.

160
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:05,780
You're even late with his payments.

161
00:09:05,950 --> 00:09:08,320
You've been disappointing me
in many ways lately.

162
00:09:09,420 --> 00:09:11,490
You're certainly not
beating around the bush.

163
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:14,860
Of course. I'll make the payments.
Just give me a little more time.

164
00:09:14,930 --> 00:09:17,530
So I guess it's true that you have
an issue with your Swiss account.

165
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:20,900
How could you say that?
You're talking to Jin Tae Seok.

166
00:09:20,970 --> 00:09:23,800
I'll give you one more week.
But that's it.

167
00:09:23,870 --> 00:09:25,300
You'll get it when I'm ready.

168
00:09:33,310 --> 00:09:36,310
Jin Tae Seok.
How dare he hang up on me?

169
00:09:37,450 --> 00:09:39,220
So he's now trying
to test the old man, is he?

170
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:41,950
He gets one week.

171
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:46,690
Perhaps it's time
to play a different card.

172
00:09:49,230 --> 00:09:52,560
I bought myself a week,
but if I miss the deadline...

173
00:09:54,170 --> 00:09:56,500
I must get that Swiss account back,
no matter what.

174
00:09:57,370 --> 00:09:59,900
Secretary Yoon!

175
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:05,380
You called for me, sir?

176
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:06,910
Tell Madam Sa to come see me.

177
00:10:09,450 --> 00:10:12,220
(Chief Director of Design Team
Jin Jung Won)

178
00:10:25,830 --> 00:10:28,270
So you made it big
by being Jin Tae Seok's lapdog.

179
00:10:28,270 --> 00:10:29,500
Did you...

180
00:10:30,300 --> 00:10:31,740
post the video, Se Hoon?

181
00:10:32,040 --> 00:10:33,370
And the public petition too?

182
00:10:33,970 --> 00:10:35,470
Does it matter who did it?

183
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:38,640
Now there's no way out
for Jin Tae Seok.

184
00:10:39,180 --> 00:10:41,050
Jung Won,
you should stop this nonsense.

185
00:10:42,010 --> 00:10:43,780
Even when you tried to run me over
with your car,

186
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:46,480
I thought you ended up like that...

187
00:10:47,250 --> 00:10:48,750
because of me.

188
00:10:50,020 --> 00:10:51,760
I kept thinking,
"How angry must he be?"

189
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:53,890
"How furious would he be?"

190
00:10:55,660 --> 00:10:56,730
But...

191
00:10:56,990 --> 00:10:59,560
- But what?
- Both you and Young Chae...

192
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:02,430
are like foxes who know
the apricots are poisoned,

193
00:11:03,030 --> 00:11:04,970
but have become tamed
by their sweet taste.

194
00:11:05,670 --> 00:11:06,670
What?

195
00:11:06,670 --> 00:11:08,870
Blind to the poison coursing
through your body,

196
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:12,480
and knowing full well
it will kill you in the end,

197
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:14,180
you still can't stop.

198
00:11:14,180 --> 00:11:15,650
You should be grateful...

199
00:11:16,150 --> 00:11:17,480
to me or to Young Chae.

200
00:11:18,250 --> 00:11:20,580
We're the ones who exposed
Jin Tae Seok's evil deeds.

201
00:11:20,890 --> 00:11:22,790
Did you really think I wanted...

202
00:11:23,420 --> 00:11:25,660
the entire world to see the moment
I was falling...

203
00:11:26,520 --> 00:11:27,930
from that rooftop?

204
00:11:29,690 --> 00:11:33,600
He's my father, my flesh and blood,
but he's so evil...

205
00:11:34,270 --> 00:11:37,130
and threw me off that rooftop
without a second thought.

206
00:11:39,170 --> 00:11:41,870
My heart breaks
into a thousand pieces every time,

207
00:11:42,870 --> 00:11:44,010
so how can you not understand that?

208
00:11:46,280 --> 00:11:47,680
And you say I should be grateful?

209
00:11:48,710 --> 00:11:49,910
Don't be ridiculous!

210
00:11:49,910 --> 00:11:52,020
You're saying you reconciled
with that monster?

211
00:11:53,050 --> 00:11:54,520
You expect me to believe that?

212
00:11:56,090 --> 00:11:59,220
I see your ploy to push me aside,
take over as heir,

213
00:11:59,420 --> 00:12:02,060
and then take down
Jin Tae Seok yourself?

214
00:12:03,930 --> 00:12:05,300
Whatever path I take,

215
00:12:06,030 --> 00:12:07,360
that's my choice
and my decision to make.

216
00:12:07,470 --> 00:12:09,970
So you should stay out of what I do.

217
00:12:11,740 --> 00:12:13,800
Every single moment,
I think about one thing.

218
00:12:14,870 --> 00:12:17,610
How to bring Jin Tae Seok
to his knees for good.

219
00:12:18,210 --> 00:12:20,080
And you, who has become Jin Jung Won,
right along with him.

220
00:12:20,140 --> 00:12:22,550
You're nothing but a monster
drowning in self-pity.

221
00:12:23,610 --> 00:12:27,590
Nothing more, nothing less,
Jin Se Hoon.

222
00:12:28,820 --> 00:12:30,620
Get out of my office now.

223
00:12:32,220 --> 00:12:35,060
It seems things are looking up
for Kunhyang these days.

224
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:38,760
I hear the Kunhyang Gallery
is holding a major exhibition.

225
00:12:39,530 --> 00:12:42,430
Isn't that artist
notoriously hard to book?

226
00:12:44,070 --> 00:12:45,440
The gallery...

227
00:12:46,140 --> 00:12:49,070
has its donations,
revenue from art sales,

228
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:51,680
and it's all thanks
to Director Cha's hard work.

229
00:12:52,580 --> 00:12:55,110
Or should I call her Chief Director
Jin Jung Won now?

230
00:12:55,310 --> 00:13:00,280
Speaking of donations,
is your family helping, Madam Sa?

231
00:13:00,350 --> 00:13:03,390
Oh, please. My father's too busy
running the country for that.

232
00:13:03,950 --> 00:13:06,820
Then where are the donations from?
Now I'm curious.

233
00:13:09,590 --> 00:13:10,730
Don't...

234
00:13:11,160 --> 00:13:14,230
- get any wild ideas.
- Wild ideas?

235
00:13:15,570 --> 00:13:16,830
I wonder what those could be.

236
00:13:16,830 --> 00:13:19,340
I left the gallery
to Hye Ra ages ago.

237
00:13:19,400 --> 00:13:20,970
I just had to ask.

238
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:23,670
I'm not deeply involved
in the operations either...

239
00:13:23,740 --> 00:13:25,040
Your brother...

240
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:28,050
was appointed to
an important party position, wasn't he?

241
00:13:28,980 --> 00:13:30,350
Last time, he even
covered his campaign funds...

242
00:13:30,350 --> 00:13:32,220
with just one painting, remember?

243
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:33,780
Why are you playing dumb?

244
00:13:33,880 --> 00:13:35,950
Not bringing up the past...

245
00:13:36,650 --> 00:13:40,020
- is an unwritten rule in our world.
- The Kunhyang Association funds.

246
00:13:41,760 --> 00:13:44,730
Haven't you heard
that they're from my Swiss account?

247
00:13:47,260 --> 00:13:49,830
I just did as Advisor Han said...

248
00:13:49,900 --> 00:13:52,570
I wonder if your brother
will enjoy prison food.

249
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:56,070
Do you think Hye Ra is powerful
enough to keep him out of prison?

250
00:14:00,180 --> 00:14:04,150
I heard Advisor Han
had the Swiss account.

251
00:14:04,220 --> 00:14:05,580
I don't know
what happened after that.

252
00:14:05,850 --> 00:14:06,850
I swear.

253
00:14:08,990 --> 00:14:10,020
Han Hye Ra.

254
00:14:10,820 --> 00:14:13,460
How dare she access my vault
without my permission?

255
00:14:13,990 --> 00:14:16,360
And she's planning to use
my own money to come for my throat?

256
00:14:20,760 --> 00:14:22,530
So you cracked
under Jin Tae Seok's threats...

257
00:14:22,900 --> 00:14:25,440
and told him I was the one
who stole the Swiss account?

258
00:14:25,540 --> 00:14:29,870
I didn't implicate
Chief Director Jin Jung Won.

259
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:32,610
Well, that's one thing
you did right.

260
00:14:33,510 --> 00:14:34,680
But, Madam Sa,

261
00:14:35,510 --> 00:14:37,620
you need to be tight-lipped
to survive.

262
00:14:38,120 --> 00:14:39,180
You've disappointed me.

263
00:14:41,190 --> 00:14:43,190
Not as disappointed as I am.

264
00:14:44,920 --> 00:14:46,860
Hye Ra, you betrayed me again?

265
00:14:47,560 --> 00:14:49,290
I have no idea
what you're talking about.

266
00:14:49,930 --> 00:14:52,360
You're doubting me again?

267
00:14:52,430 --> 00:14:54,600
I'm trying to figure out
what to do with you, Hye Ra.

268
00:14:55,800 --> 00:14:57,970
After you've already
clipped my wings?

269
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,700
This is just like you.

270
00:15:01,540 --> 00:15:04,380
You never bother to ask
why I did it, do you?

271
00:15:04,940 --> 00:15:06,240
Why did you do it?

272
00:15:06,410 --> 00:15:09,910
You use love as an excuse
to keep me tied down and caged.

273
00:15:10,210 --> 00:15:11,450
It's suffocating.

274
00:15:12,450 --> 00:15:14,850
Being treated
like some decorative houseplant,

275
00:15:15,750 --> 00:15:17,090
I can't take it anymore.

276
00:15:17,450 --> 00:15:19,420
So you stole my slush fund?

277
00:15:19,860 --> 00:15:21,730
You know how important
that money is.

278
00:15:22,060 --> 00:15:24,760
Without that money, I'm done for.

279
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:29,670
I knew it.

280
00:15:30,170 --> 00:15:32,000
I was right to take it from you.

281
00:15:32,400 --> 00:15:33,400
What did you just say?

282
00:15:33,670 --> 00:15:34,810
You still don't get it?

283
00:15:37,510 --> 00:15:40,080
I'm the one holding your leash now.

284
00:15:42,150 --> 00:15:44,480
Forget about your little houseplant.

285
00:15:45,180 --> 00:15:48,490
I have you wrapped
around my little finger,

286
00:15:48,720 --> 00:15:50,320
and I'm just toying with you.

287
00:15:50,520 --> 00:15:51,760
Han Hye Ra.

288
00:15:52,560 --> 00:15:55,830
Did you really take
that Swiss account?

289
00:15:56,160 --> 00:15:57,360
I already told you I did.

290
00:15:57,490 --> 00:15:58,800
But why?

291
00:16:01,600 --> 00:16:03,700
Because I wanted to be free of you.

292
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:07,300
But I love you so much.

293
00:16:07,770 --> 00:16:09,710
Why would you want to be free of me?

294
00:16:10,410 --> 00:16:13,140
By stealing my slush fund,
my very lifeline?

295
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:17,380
You should've just lied.
Why did you have to admit it?

296
00:16:19,280 --> 00:16:20,850
Because I don't have it anymore.

297
00:16:20,980 --> 00:16:22,050
What?

298
00:16:22,520 --> 00:16:23,750
What are you talking about?

299
00:16:23,890 --> 00:16:25,220
Someone else took it.

300
00:16:26,390 --> 00:16:28,030
They even changed the password.

301
00:16:28,490 --> 00:16:29,790
Who did it?

302
00:16:30,860 --> 00:16:31,860
I think...

303
00:16:34,300 --> 00:16:35,470
Gong Nan Sook did it.

304
00:16:36,300 --> 00:16:37,500
Gong Nan Sook?

305
00:16:38,600 --> 00:16:42,840
When I stole your account,
I told Gong Nan Sook.

306
00:16:43,010 --> 00:16:44,110
And then she...

307
00:16:44,780 --> 00:16:48,150
How can I trust people?
I only trust money.

308
00:16:48,280 --> 00:16:51,120
No, just split it in half
and send it to my account.

309
00:16:52,050 --> 00:16:53,880
They call her "Money Nan Sook"
for a reason.

310
00:16:56,150 --> 00:16:58,220
First, I need to
get the Swiss account back,

311
00:16:58,460 --> 00:17:00,160
and then you and I can talk.

312
00:17:05,630 --> 00:17:09,070
Go have a bloody, knock-down,
drag-out fight with Gong Nan Sook.

313
00:17:09,670 --> 00:17:12,370
And then, like a defeated soldier,

314
00:17:13,170 --> 00:17:14,940
get on your knees before Jung Won...

315
00:17:15,210 --> 00:17:17,640
and beg her for help, Jin Tae Seok.

316
00:17:26,950 --> 00:17:31,050
I got off work early for once
and was trying to relax.

317
00:17:31,120 --> 00:17:34,120
Why did you drag me out?
This is such a pain, seriously.

318
00:17:34,990 --> 00:17:38,000
You need to leave.
That is Chairman Gong's seat.

319
00:17:39,230 --> 00:17:40,760
Get him out of my face,
Gong Nan Sook.

320
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:42,300
Get me out of here?

321
00:17:42,770 --> 00:17:45,640
Yeong Soo,
just step aside for a moment.

322
00:17:51,040 --> 00:17:52,740
Are you here
because of the Swiss account?

323
00:17:53,040 --> 00:17:55,310
If that's what this is about,
you're a step too late.

324
00:17:55,410 --> 00:17:59,220
Come on, haven't you heard of
"better late than never?"

325
00:17:59,280 --> 00:18:02,550
I only took exactly half
of that money.

326
00:18:02,620 --> 00:18:05,460
Han Hye Ra's people
are still managing the account.

327
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:06,920
Han Hye Ra's people?

328
00:18:08,890 --> 00:18:10,390
You're saying Hye Ra
didn't do it alone?

329
00:18:12,360 --> 00:18:14,400
I don't know,
maybe she had her assistant do it.

330
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:15,870
I have no idea. I wasn't involved.

331
00:18:16,270 --> 00:18:18,100
Gong Nan Sook, spit it out!

332
00:18:18,840 --> 00:18:22,310
Who helped Hye Ra? Tell me!

333
00:18:23,540 --> 00:18:25,980
To be blunt, it's just a slush fund.

334
00:18:25,980 --> 00:18:29,080
If you use your usual dirty tricks,
you'll have it back in no time.

335
00:18:29,750 --> 00:18:32,650
Half of it gone is no big deal,
is it?

336
00:18:32,980 --> 00:18:37,250
You should be glad I left some,
shouldn't you?

337
00:18:38,790 --> 00:18:40,160
Cough up the money now.

338
00:18:40,590 --> 00:18:44,460
I bet some big shot is probably
seeing red,

339
00:18:44,460 --> 00:18:47,800
waiting for that money, am I right?

340
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:52,970
Once I get my hands on money,

341
00:18:53,040 --> 00:18:55,340
I never spit it back out.

342
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:57,310
You'd probably have to kill me
to get it.

343
00:18:58,940 --> 00:19:02,980
You'd better sweet-talk Han Hye Ra
if you want to keep the rest of it.

344
00:19:03,380 --> 00:19:06,120
I don't know who this big shot is,

345
00:19:06,450 --> 00:19:08,220
but if you don't pay on time,

346
00:19:08,290 --> 00:19:09,620
you're in for a world of trouble.

347
00:19:10,090 --> 00:19:12,790
Jin Tae Seok, maybe you should
start getting your coffin ready.

348
00:19:12,790 --> 00:19:13,990
Why, you...

349
00:19:25,070 --> 00:19:27,700
You hacked the Swiss account,
right, Manager Gu?

350
00:19:28,840 --> 00:19:30,340
You already knew?

351
00:19:30,410 --> 00:19:34,110
I knew that Madam Gong took
half of the slush fund.

352
00:19:35,750 --> 00:19:37,550
Yes, that's correct.

353
00:19:39,880 --> 00:19:43,390
I already knew you were loyal
to Madam Gong,

354
00:19:43,450 --> 00:19:45,090
but I never thought you'd stab me
in the back like this.

355
00:19:47,090 --> 00:19:49,090
I admit, this time I did regret it.

356
00:19:50,230 --> 00:19:54,230
But if the same situation arose,
I would make the same choice again.

357
00:19:54,330 --> 00:19:57,670
- You'll stick with Gong Nan Sook?
- I'm sorry.

358
00:20:07,680 --> 00:20:09,080
Did Han Hye Ra tell you?

359
00:20:09,450 --> 00:20:12,020
That I made off
with half the slush fund?

360
00:20:12,080 --> 00:20:13,820
Are you still this greedy for money?

361
00:20:14,850 --> 00:20:16,750
You have more money
than you know what to do with.

362
00:20:16,820 --> 00:20:19,060
Why would you risk your life for it?

363
00:20:19,120 --> 00:20:21,890
I'll worry about my own life.

364
00:20:22,230 --> 00:20:23,760
You're the one taking the risks.

365
00:20:23,760 --> 00:20:25,200
Are you actually worried about me?

366
00:20:26,060 --> 00:20:30,300
That's the thing. I don't know why,
but whenever I think of you,

367
00:20:30,730 --> 00:20:34,740
I get so anxious,
like watching a child wander off.

368
00:20:35,840 --> 00:20:37,940
I'm afraid I won't be able
to ease your worries, Mother.

369
00:20:38,910 --> 00:20:40,680
Because I'm going to risk my life
to fight him.

370
00:20:41,580 --> 00:20:42,780
I'm betting the rest of my life...

371
00:20:43,550 --> 00:20:46,050
on destroying Jin Tae Seok.

372
00:20:48,020 --> 00:20:50,150
Then my life is in your hands too.

373
00:20:50,950 --> 00:20:52,220
What's that supposed to mean?

374
00:20:52,220 --> 00:20:53,560
Twenty-five years ago,

375
00:20:54,360 --> 00:20:56,360
I came to owe you my life.

376
00:21:04,100 --> 00:21:07,870
I just wanted to live
like I was on top of the world,

377
00:21:09,070 --> 00:21:11,240
but I ended up killing someone
with my own two hands.

378
00:21:11,780 --> 00:21:15,780
No matter what a scumbag he was,
he was Ha Neul's father.

379
00:21:17,380 --> 00:21:19,280
I don't deserve to live.

380
00:21:20,950 --> 00:21:22,120
No, Mom.

381
00:21:23,390 --> 00:21:25,290
Don't you disappear on me too.

382
00:21:25,560 --> 00:21:27,990
Stay alive and be my mom, please.

383
00:21:36,900 --> 00:21:39,200
- Do you remember that?
- Well...

384
00:21:40,570 --> 00:21:43,770
Is that why you always treated me
more like a son than your own?

385
00:21:43,940 --> 00:21:45,410
I can't deny it.

386
00:21:45,610 --> 00:21:47,410
Then please listen to me.

387
00:21:48,910 --> 00:21:51,350
That slush fund in the Swiss account
is dangerous.

388
00:21:51,620 --> 00:21:52,780
Madam Gong, no,

389
00:21:53,450 --> 00:21:55,890
Mother,
it could ruin your entire life.

390
00:21:56,690 --> 00:21:57,750
Give it back to me.

391
00:21:58,920 --> 00:22:00,390
Won't it be dangerous for you?

392
00:22:01,890 --> 00:22:04,760
I'm going to get
the most dangerous person on our side.

393
00:22:05,530 --> 00:22:08,170
- I'll meet with them.
- They won't listen to you, Mother.

394
00:22:09,130 --> 00:22:10,470
Wait, when you say "them,"

395
00:22:11,700 --> 00:22:13,500
are you talking about the people...

396
00:22:14,600 --> 00:22:16,440
at the very top?

397
00:22:26,080 --> 00:22:28,750
Do you think Gong Nan Sook gets it?

398
00:22:29,920 --> 00:22:31,990
She's highly unpredictable.

399
00:22:32,390 --> 00:22:34,260
The account password
has been changed,

400
00:22:34,260 --> 00:22:36,790
so she is locked out.

401
00:22:36,990 --> 00:22:39,700
True. It's less about
how much is in the slush fund...

402
00:22:39,800 --> 00:22:42,370
and more about
who's in control of it.

403
00:22:43,100 --> 00:22:46,000
- What about the video?
- It was Young Chae and Se Hoon.

404
00:22:46,270 --> 00:22:49,640
This will have devastating fallout
for Jin Tae Seok.

405
00:22:50,410 --> 00:22:54,280
Defeating Jin Tae Seok is the goal,
but it's too soon.

406
00:22:55,250 --> 00:22:58,010
We've shattered the poisoned chalice
too soon.

407
00:22:58,250 --> 00:23:00,850
This could easily blow up
the entire succession plan.

408
00:23:01,250 --> 00:23:02,450
The timing is all wrong.

409
00:23:02,620 --> 00:23:04,520
We can't let our guard down
with Madam Gong either.

410
00:23:04,820 --> 00:23:08,460
If Kunhyang's structure fractures,
the board led by Madam Gong...

411
00:23:08,530 --> 00:23:09,990
will seize control of the company.

412
00:23:10,360 --> 00:23:14,030
Jin Tae Seok wants complete control
of every situation.

413
00:23:14,770 --> 00:23:15,870
But...

414
00:23:16,470 --> 00:23:20,200
his fortress is crumbling,
and he must be losing his mind.

415
00:23:22,270 --> 00:23:25,310
We need to use his desire
for control against him...

416
00:23:26,310 --> 00:23:27,410
somehow.

417
00:23:32,180 --> 00:23:37,020
Grandma, this baddest woman
could be taken down in an instant.

418
00:23:37,420 --> 00:23:40,120
Am I really going to be okay
just sitting back and doing nothing?

419
00:23:41,960 --> 00:23:45,230
Why did you let those lowlifes in?
I told you to kick them out.

420
00:23:45,500 --> 00:23:49,330
But you get attached to people.
Young Chae is still my daughter.

421
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:51,800
How could I stand in the way
when she's crazy about him?

422
00:23:51,870 --> 00:23:55,510
This is why I can't give up on you,
sweetheart.

423
00:23:56,410 --> 00:23:59,880
You act tough,
but you're a real softy inside.

424
00:24:01,310 --> 00:24:03,550
That's why I admire Chairman Gong.

425
00:24:04,650 --> 00:24:08,890
I don't care how.
Just find a way to get me out alive.

426
00:24:10,820 --> 00:24:12,760
She says there are two options.

427
00:24:14,090 --> 00:24:15,130
What are they?

428
00:24:15,390 --> 00:24:17,160
Give the money back.

429
00:24:18,360 --> 00:24:19,460
No way.

430
00:24:20,130 --> 00:24:22,100
Even if I died ten times
and were born a hundred times,

431
00:24:22,100 --> 00:24:23,930
I could never do that.

432
00:24:24,470 --> 00:24:26,670
Then you have no choice.
Get rid of them.

433
00:24:28,540 --> 00:24:30,610
Get rid of what? Who?

434
00:24:33,840 --> 00:24:36,010
You mean, Young Chae?

435
00:24:36,410 --> 00:24:38,450
I wasn't told the details.

436
00:24:38,650 --> 00:24:41,590
She said to let
the most fearsome person in the world...

437
00:24:41,590 --> 00:24:42,750
do whatever they want.

438
00:24:43,220 --> 00:24:44,620
The most fearsome person
in the world?

439
00:24:45,190 --> 00:24:48,360
There are so many fearsome people.
Darn it, this is so confusing.

440
00:24:48,890 --> 00:24:49,890
Who is it?

441
00:24:58,500 --> 00:25:00,470
Why did you tell me to come here
in the middle of the night?

442
00:25:01,200 --> 00:25:02,440
To give back the money?

443
00:25:02,740 --> 00:25:05,740
I never spit out money
I've already taken.

444
00:25:05,810 --> 00:25:07,780
That's my golden rule.
How many times must I tell you?

445
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:10,510
Then...

446
00:25:11,180 --> 00:25:12,920
what kind of game are you playing?

447
00:25:14,080 --> 00:25:18,290
Maybe there's something I can do
instead of giving you money.

448
00:25:18,490 --> 00:25:20,820
Do you know
who has the Swiss account?

449
00:25:20,890 --> 00:25:22,560
Obviously,
it's either Han Hye Ra or me.

450
00:25:22,560 --> 00:25:24,490
Hye Ra said it was you!

451
00:25:25,300 --> 00:25:29,430
Who you believe is up to you,
Jin Tae Seok.

452
00:25:30,930 --> 00:25:31,940
Fine.

453
00:25:32,740 --> 00:25:36,140
That bastard, Se Hoon,
who tried to poison and kill me.

454
00:25:36,810 --> 00:25:37,810
Will you get rid of him for me?

455
00:25:38,710 --> 00:25:42,010
I have been debating
whether I should.

456
00:25:42,950 --> 00:25:46,120
If I do, then I get half
of that slush fund.

457
00:25:50,550 --> 00:25:52,190
I only have five days left.

458
00:25:53,090 --> 00:25:56,030
If I don't get that account back
by then,

459
00:25:56,360 --> 00:25:58,160
I could be completely ruined.

460
00:26:00,660 --> 00:26:02,930
Are you actually scared?

461
00:26:12,110 --> 00:26:13,180
You wanted to see me?

462
00:26:13,680 --> 00:26:17,280
You know who has the Swiss account,
don't you?

463
00:26:17,850 --> 00:26:19,420
What makes you think that?

464
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:22,620
Gong Nan Sook only cares for money.
She wouldn't leverage the account.

465
00:26:22,750 --> 00:26:25,020
Then it must be Jin Se Hoon,

466
00:26:25,520 --> 00:26:27,320
or Advisor Han Hye Ra.

467
00:26:28,120 --> 00:26:29,630
Get it for me.

468
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:33,800
- How am I supposed to do that?
- Only you can do it.

469
00:26:35,530 --> 00:26:36,770
Is this a test?

470
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:39,900
If you want to live,
I have to survive.

471
00:26:46,810 --> 00:26:49,980
Let go! I said to let me go!

472
00:26:50,350 --> 00:26:52,450
Why are you doing this?

473
00:26:52,580 --> 00:26:54,880
I'm sorry, but you have to disappear
so that Young Chae can live.

474
00:26:54,950 --> 00:26:56,650
- And for my sake as well.
- Mom!

475
00:26:56,650 --> 00:26:58,420
Do you want to watch me go crazy?

476
00:26:58,620 --> 00:27:00,160
You're already crazy.

477
00:27:00,160 --> 00:27:01,890
Manager Gu, hurry and take him away.

478
00:27:01,890 --> 00:27:04,560
- Yes.
- Mother!

479
00:27:04,890 --> 00:27:06,230
Let go of me!

480
00:27:06,500 --> 00:27:07,600
Mother!

481
00:27:16,540 --> 00:27:18,010
We have five days left.

482
00:27:18,740 --> 00:27:19,980
What are your orders, sir?

483
00:27:21,710 --> 00:27:22,850
You want my opinion?

484
00:27:24,410 --> 00:27:27,850
I believe it's time
we cut Jin Tae Seok loose...

485
00:27:29,620 --> 00:27:31,420
if he can't keep his promise
this time.

486
00:27:38,800 --> 00:27:40,930
- Where's Father?
- In his study.

487
00:27:41,870 --> 00:27:45,670
He seems to have a lot on his mind.
He's been in there for hours.

488
00:27:57,810 --> 00:27:58,820
Jin Tae Seok.

489
00:27:59,150 --> 00:28:02,650
Did you forget who allowed you
to control the Kunhyang Group?

490
00:28:02,890 --> 00:28:04,850
Whatever it takes,
cover the losses and send it now.

491
00:28:05,920 --> 00:28:06,960
Chief Kim.

492
00:28:07,760 --> 00:28:09,660
He's slowly tightening the noose.

493
00:28:10,130 --> 00:28:12,730
Otherwise,
I can't cover for you anymore.

494
00:28:13,760 --> 00:28:15,500
This could end up going the way
of the public petition.

495
00:28:17,500 --> 00:28:20,400
We'll just find a new channel.

496
00:28:28,850 --> 00:28:30,050
What's wrong, Father?

497
00:28:31,310 --> 00:28:32,620
Jung Won, my daughter.

498
00:28:33,250 --> 00:28:35,450
You're the only one who can save me,
Jung Won.

499
00:28:36,120 --> 00:28:37,590
Please, save me, Jung Won.

500
00:28:38,460 --> 00:28:39,690
What do you mean?

501
00:28:40,390 --> 00:28:41,960
I don't have that kind of power.

502
00:28:41,960 --> 00:28:43,430
My power is your power.

503
00:28:44,230 --> 00:28:46,060
Right now, if I get involved,
no one will believe me.

504
00:28:46,460 --> 00:28:47,730
But you're different.

505
00:28:48,770 --> 00:28:50,330
I may be the one behind you,

506
00:28:50,870 --> 00:28:53,200
but it's you
the people and the public see.

507
00:28:53,840 --> 00:28:57,240
You're younger and more vibrant,
and they have high hopes for you.

508
00:28:57,410 --> 00:29:00,710
If you're going to ask for a favor,
Father, do it properly.

509
00:29:01,810 --> 00:29:04,310
- What?
- Tell me what you need me to do,

510
00:29:04,910 --> 00:29:07,050
and what I get in return.

511
00:29:07,620 --> 00:29:09,120
Try making a proper deal with me.

512
00:29:09,990 --> 00:29:10,990
That's the way you do best, Dad.

513
00:29:16,190 --> 00:29:17,190
What?

514
00:29:17,760 --> 00:29:20,330
You're going to say yourself
that the video was fake?

515
00:29:20,800 --> 00:29:21,800
That's right.

516
00:29:22,370 --> 00:29:25,400
It's the only way it can look like
I'm saving Jin Tae Seok.

517
00:29:25,770 --> 00:29:28,300
Jung Won, how can you
say that yourself?

518
00:29:28,970 --> 00:29:32,540
How can you say it was fake?
We know it was traumatic for you.

519
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:33,740
How could I ever forget?

520
00:29:33,940 --> 00:29:36,650
Jung Won,
you don't have to go that far.

521
00:29:37,080 --> 00:29:38,210
You're only human.

522
00:29:38,980 --> 00:29:40,850
Your own father
tried to have you killed.

523
00:29:41,680 --> 00:29:43,150
The whole world needs to know.

524
00:29:43,820 --> 00:29:45,990
I absolutely will not allow it.

525
00:29:45,990 --> 00:29:47,090
I'm against it too.

526
00:29:48,890 --> 00:29:51,660
This is my choice and decision.

527
00:29:52,760 --> 00:29:53,760
Please, trust me,

528
00:29:54,300 --> 00:29:56,400
Mom and Ha Neul.

529
00:30:04,810 --> 00:30:06,610
If I announce the video was faked,

530
00:30:07,410 --> 00:30:08,910
what can you offer me, Dad?

531
00:30:09,310 --> 00:30:10,410
Tell me what you want.

532
00:30:11,850 --> 00:30:15,820
Give me the details
of your slush fund accounts.

533
00:30:16,350 --> 00:30:17,350
What?

534
00:30:22,490 --> 00:30:23,830
That's my girl.

535
00:30:24,330 --> 00:30:27,200
It's a true businessman's deal.
That's how it should be.

536
00:30:29,270 --> 00:30:30,770
You do what I want first.

537
00:30:31,570 --> 00:30:34,270
And then I'll accept your offer.

538
00:30:35,570 --> 00:30:36,740
You'd better keep your promise.

539
00:30:37,870 --> 00:30:40,040
Because if you don't,

540
00:30:40,540 --> 00:30:42,250
I'll confess
that the video is real myself.

541
00:31:00,060 --> 00:31:03,100
(A Graceful Liar)

542
00:31:25,220 --> 00:31:27,090
You really don't know
who has the slush fund account?

543
00:31:27,160 --> 00:31:29,130
I'm the one
who has the Swiss account.

544
00:31:29,190 --> 00:31:32,100
So you lied just
to take down Jin Tae Seok.

545
00:31:32,200 --> 00:31:34,560
That's my daughter, Jin Jung Won.

546
00:31:34,730 --> 00:31:36,800
I never thought Jung Won
would go this far.

547
00:31:36,870 --> 00:31:39,740
I'm telling you,
I wish I had met her sooner.

548
00:31:39,940 --> 00:31:41,540
Where's Se Hoon?

549
00:31:41,600 --> 00:31:44,210
I took care of Jin Se Hoon
just as you wanted.

550
00:31:44,510 --> 00:31:45,940
I told you to just get rid of him!

551
00:31:46,080 --> 00:31:48,110
Our communication channel
with Kunhyang Group...

552
00:31:48,110 --> 00:31:49,980
has changed, Jin Tae Seok.

553
00:31:50,080 --> 00:31:52,280
They dare throw me away?

554
00:31:56,490 --> 00:31:58,450
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
